      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must hold ISO 9001 certification and documented V&V test suite covering all flow regimes relevant to the pump geometry.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver holds ISO 9001 certification and a documented regression test suite exists, but coverage of high-shear impeller-tip flows is incomplete. Achieved level 3 falls below the required level 4 for MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
