      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model inputs characterized with probability distributions; Monte Carlo UQ performed with at least 500 samples; sensitivity indices reported.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was performed with 512 LHS samples propagating uncertainty in viscosity, density, and rotational speed. Hemolysis model constants were treated as fixed (not uncertain), and geometric manufacturing tolerances were excluded from the UQ, limiting the factor to level 3."
