      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test samples (blood analogue batches) must be characterized for viscosity and density; batch-to-batch variability must be reported.",
      "rationale": "Batch characterization data for the glycerol-water analogue were not available in the experimental dataset obtained from the FDA pump study archive. No batch-to-batch variability information was retrievable. This factor could not be meaningfully assessed; achieved level defaulted to 1."
